  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Level 2</strong> Transmutation</p>\n<p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 bonus</p>\n<p><strong>Range:</strong> undefined touch</p>\n<p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (a hot pepper)</p>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong> Concentration, up to 1 minute</p>\n\nYou touch one willing creature, and choose Acid, Cold, Fire, Lightning, or Poison. Until the spell ends, the target can take a Magic|XPHB action to exhale a 15-foot Cone [Area of Effect]|XPHB|Cone. Each creature in that area makes a Dexterity saving throw, taking 3d6 damage of the chosen type on a failed save or half as much damage on a successful one.\n\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels:</strong> The damage increases by 3d6|2-9|1d6 for each spell slot level above 2.</p>",
